quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,10,"Àrùn kan wà nínú ọkàn wọn{1}, nítorí náà Allāhu ṣe àlékún àrùn (náà) fún wọn. Ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro sì wà fún wọn nítorí pé wọ́n ń parọ́..",1:[Àrùn iyèméjì àti ìṣojúméjì sí āyah al-Ƙur’ān.]
  2,11,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá sọ fún wọn pé: “Ẹ má ṣèbàjẹ́ lórí ilẹ̀.” Wọ́n á wí pé: “Àwa kúkú ni alátùn-únṣe.”"
  2,12,"Ẹ kíyè sí i! Dájúdájú àwọn gan-an ni òbìlẹ̀jẹ́, ṣùgbọ́n wọn kò fura."